Entries.default: "You want to make a wager. Come, you'll enjoy it."
"Cheers to grand fortune and the Captain Furrante."
"Have a draught of the black strap. It is the finest you will ever drink."
"Weeks I have waited for this reprieve."
"The svef here is marvelous, is it not?"
"Is it me, or does Harker have a grudge against us?"
"I find the magic show rather... disappointing."
